727603f-b.title: Queens: Northern Boulevard - 78th Street
727603f-b.text:
Northern Boulevard, at the N.E. corner of 78th Street, showing two views of the J.P. Fowler house of 1873. In 190 Stuart Hirschman was the owner. It was demolished in Oct. 1925. Beyond this house is a new development facing on 79th Street.
May 1923
View 21 March 1924.
Euuogene L. Armbruster Collection
